text: Ameena Begum, also known as Dr. Ameena Shafiq, is a Bangladeshis politician and former member of parliament. She was a member of the Jatiya Sangshad from 2001 to 2006, from women's reserved seat-31 (national 331) for the Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami. == References == Category:Living people Category:Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politicians Category:Politicians from Sylhet Division Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
